Scroll to top with nice jquery scroll effect and get a nice browser slider
== Description ==
This plugin will add a nice scroll to top icon on a scrollable page and will add a nice colourful browser scroll on chrome.
== Installation ==

1. Upload the 'Smooth-scroll-to-top' folder to your '/wp-content/plugins/ directory or simply install via WordPress Dashboard
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
3. You are done...visit any page & enjoy nice scroll to top plugin

== Frequently Asked Questions ==

= Can I Change the scroll Icon?=

Yes.You can add a icon via ftp/cpanel.You have to replace scroll-img.png image on plugins/smooth-scroll-to-top/images folder.Make sure that your image is same name and its size is 35 by 35 


